<task id="task-8341" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">The Query Builder</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context ">The&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-query-builder" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;function allows you to find the desired test cases based on certain criteria.</context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">You can find the&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-query-builder" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;function while working with test suites, for example, in a dynamic test suite. See also:<xref href="../../Manage_Tests/Dynamic_Test_Suite/manage-dynamic-test-suite-ks/c_intro_dynamic-test-suite-ks.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Dynamic Test Suite</xref>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image href="Images/query-builder.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The query builder</alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To use the&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-query-builder" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;function, click on the&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-query-builder" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;button. The&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-query-builder" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;dialog appears.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Input your search criteria, then click&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-search" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="500" href="Images/query-builder-dialog.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The query builder dialog</alt></image></info><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><p class="- topic/p ">The Query Builder menu includes:</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "><uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-id" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/></b>: to search the exact IDs of the test artifact</li><li class="- topic/li "><uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-name" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>: to search by the name of the test artifact</li><li class="- topic/li "><uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-description" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>: to search by the description associated with the test artifact</li><li class="- topic/li "><uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-comment" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>: to search by the comments attached to the test artifacts</li><li class="- topic/li "><uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Tag</uicontrol>: to search by the tag linked to the test artifacts</li></ul><note class="- topic/note "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li ">Every field in this Query Builder mode can be applied to search for all types of test artifacts such as test cases, test suites, folders, etc.</li><li class="- topic/li ">You can only search for one keyword at a time when searching by tag, description, or comment.</li></ul></note></info></step></steps></taskbody></task>